          <h2 class="heading staticSectionHeading nova uppercaseTitle with-line"><span>HOW TO MAKE <br class="visible-phone">"EDIBLE ROSES"</span></h2>
          <div class="staticTextWrap">
            <p>生み出し、育て、抽出する</p>
          </div>
